ă transformer.a+ - Single-head scaled dot-product attention
ă Small vocab (10 tokens), 4 samples, 2-dim embeddings

ă Softmax function: softmax_i = exp(x_i) / sum(exp(x_j))
softmax{vec}: {
  nÎ vec
  nűn[0]
  expsűn Î 0
  sumű0
  iű0
  while (i<n) {
    exps[i]ű*vec[i]
    suműsum+exps[i]
    iűi+1
  }
  iű0
  while (i<n) {
    exps[i]űexps[i]ßsum
    iűi+1
  }
  exps
}

ă Test softmax: should sum to ~1
svűsoftmax{1 2 3}
sű+/sv
if ((s>0.99)Á(s<1.01)) { Ő"[PASS] softmax sums to ~1" } else { Ő"[FAIL] softmax sum" }

