ă Weight matrices: Wq, Wk, Wv each 2x2
Wqű2 2 Î 0.50 0.20 0.10 0.40
Wkű2 2 Î 0.30 0.70 0.20 0.50
Wvű2 2 Î 0.60 0.10 0.30 0.80

ă Compute Q, K, V: each 4x2 via matrix multiply
QűX +.Á Wq
KűX +.Á Wk
VűX +.Á Wv

ă Scaled dot-product attention: scores = Q @ K^T / sqrt(d_k)
d_kű2
scaleűd_k*0.5
scoresű4 4 Î 0
iű0
while (i<4) {
  jű0
  while (j<4) {
    dotű0.0
    kű0
    while (k<d_k) {
